92
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,760
I still have to interrogate tonight.

93
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,520
So, I won't be going back.

94
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:36,640
I'll have someone take you home.

95
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,360
I...

96
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:47,560
(What do I lack compared to Qin Shiyue?)

97
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,440
(If she weren't here,)

98
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,840
(he'd surely be with me.)

99
